{"tid":2456541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外國人離港潮：去留之間， 他們怎看黯淡的城市未來？","createTime":"2021-03-22T04:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T08:02:47.000Z","uid":313113,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a30add3d3ac70ec5274d5fcc5f915128065ee5f4","tid":2456541,"uid":313113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>外國人離港潮：去留之間， 他們怎看黯淡的城市未來？</strong>｜香港｜深度｜端傳媒 <br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">免費LINK:</span></span> <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20210322-hongkong-expats-foreigners-leaving/invite_token/nQEVCEoAqt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20210322-hongkong-expats-foreigners-leaving%2Finvite_token%2FnQEVCEoAqt&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=fb6fae16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20210322-hongkong-expats-foreigners-leaving/invite_token/nQEVCEoAqt</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qryjgb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQryjgb6.jpg&h=3c86cef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「中國的確在令香港變成中國樞紐，而不是國際樞紐。所以我想的問題就是，當香港最終變成像北京、上海一樣的城市時，香港的獨特性在哪兒呢？」對於香港近年的政治變化，來自澳洲的Ivan同樣顯得理性抽離。他最初覺得香港開始失去那種迷人的生命力，是2014年雨傘運動後。他把房子賣了，因為覺得香港黯淡了，空氣彌漫著不快樂。<br />\nIvan還告訴記者，說不會普通話已經很難在香港金融業找工作、白人上司已經像恐龍一樣絕種了&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n而來自歐洲的Eric一直認為香港是個海納百川、融匯各種文化的海港，這是香港繁盛的原因，但當運動時，當他目睹警察對市民採用不必要的暴力，讓他感到一種截然不同的「不安全感」。<br />\n<br />\n一班外國人裏，有總是來又去的流動專才；也有住了十幾年懂得柯打「凍檸茶少甜」的白皮膚香港人。他們曾衝著香港的金錢、自由、異國情調而來，卻又因著什麼原因離開？他們中還有人會留下來繼續看香港的潮起潮落嗎？"},{"pid":"5e601679d8dfb34a1571e01a97c627ed519f1415","tid":2456541,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a693d59dd87847e05805879b85155c181c4bc44f","tid":2456541,"uid":152705,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:04:47.000Z","msg":"正, 又可以請番個支那人頂替加速換血。<br />\n<br />\n港豬話快d移民, 自己可以上位。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28adf1168cc7c2fe2efe8dee669cf59704a5ebb","tid":2456541,"uid":8662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d5e6e8b9bd7e56e91354aff0c74f7cae0a6214","tid":2456541,"uid":65027,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a693d59dd87847e05805879b85155c181c4bc44f","tid":2456541,"uid":152705,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:04:47.000Z","msg":"正, 又可以請番個支那人頂替加速換血。<br />\n<br />\n港豬話快d移民, 自己可以上位。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港豬以為食移民潮可得益，但中共有當港豬係自己人嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86c3afc6f7bcde5112a101c8bf5208178eb58c0","tid":2456541,"uid":152705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"53d5e6e8b9bd7e56e91354aff0c74f7cae0a6214","tid":2456541,"uid":65027,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a693d59dd87847e05805879b85155c181c4bc44f","tid":2456541,"uid":152705,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:04:47.000Z","msg":"正, 又可以請番個支那人頂替加速換血。<br />\n<br />\n港豬話快d移民, 自己可以上位。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl